        [
          "You've been told by others of your clan that an elder has set LA up as a safe place for Assamites. You don't know if that's true or not, but you are here and you may as well make it true."
        ],
        [
          "You are a soldier and fighter first and foremost. LA is supposedly currently at peace, but you know there are things that are hunting the likes of you out there. It's far better to be prepared than not. Offer your services."
        ],
        [
          "Find out if there is any truth to some of the crazy stories you've heard out there. Being better informed means you can be better armed."
